original_title: Mystic Vibrosis - A Guide To Living Indubiously
overview: 2 brothers born with a disease called Cystic Fibrosis have persevered to not only survive their illness, but find their purpose while being catapulted onto the world stage as a powerful force for change through their band, Indubious.
title: Mystic Vibrosis - A Guide To Living Indubiously
